              </p>
              <p className="text-base leading-relaxed text-text-body sm:text-lg">
                我们将采取 Build in public 的形式，透明公开化活动推进和财务流程，将赞助费 100% 用于参赛者和体验者，让技术和创造本身成为主角。
              </p>
            </div>
            <div className="space-y-6">
              <div className="flex gap-4">
                <div className="flex-shrink-0">
                  <div className="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-accent-blue/10">
                    <MapPin className="h-5 w-5 text-accent-blue" />
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h3 className="mb-2 font-semibold text-text-head">
                    天津首个本地化黑客松
                  </h3>
                  <p className="text-sm text-text-body">
                    具备强烈的城市符号和媒体关注度
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div className="flex gap-4">
                <div className="flex-shrink-0">
                  <div className="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-accent-blue/10">
                    <Users className="h-5 w-5 text-accent-blue" />
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h3 className="mb-2 font-semibold text-text-head">
                    覆盖高质量参与者
                  </h3>
                  <p className="text-sm text-text-body">
                    覆盖天津及周边城市高校学生、年轻开发者、AI初创企业等高质量参与者
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div className="flex gap-4">
                <div className="flex-shrink-0">
                  <div className="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-accent-blue/10">
                    <Heart className="h-5 w-5 text-accent-blue" />
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h3 className="mb-2 font-semibold text-text-head">
